{"tid":1949166,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★上海理髮店月蝕逾4萬元　經營40年不敵疫情明日結業","createTime":"2020-03-29T12:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T15:02:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ed549ac0aebc2151a51b06877e3803c2470d9ee1","tid":1949166,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:45:34.000Z","msg":"在新冠肺炎疫情衝擊下，各行各業大受打擊，其中位於北角渣華道近40年的上海僑冠理髮店更不敵肺炎疫情，被迫於明日（30日）結業。理髮店老闆高先生指生意受疫情影響，大跌三分之二，過去兩個月平均每月虧蝕至少4萬港元，於數日前決定結業。他又指鋪位租金每月約7萬港元，即使業主願意減租也決定結業，稱「冇本錢蝕啊」、「減租都做唔掂」。至於未來路向，他表示會繼續尋找工作，但未有考慮「重出江湖」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200329/bkn-20200329171422083-0329_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200329%2Fbkn-20200329171422083-0329_00822_001.html&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqzw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=9e4545b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200329/bkn-20200329171422083-0329_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"276a23540ceb63374b42ee26ecfa85e0f44ca8c1","tid":1949166,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6jzYzm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6jzYzm.gif&h=5c9a3118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a93f1984264a18dbf7ffc7256ba01689828a1bd8","tid":1949166,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee833ad120966936a89c4927a9580702abe19e8c","tid":1949166,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:52:37.000Z","msg":"上海理髮一個月要剪幾多個人先夠俾租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4150d900417cdf534be29579935e5982da66059","tid":1949166,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":